title: Netflix List March 2017 - What’s Coming To/Leaving Netflix in March
text:
This was the day I was nervous as hell going into @Netflix for the first time to talk about @13reasonswhy -my mom found this book in 2009 and worked her ass off to make it with me, guide me and tell this story authentically (the only reason, beside Jay this project was even made)
A post shared by Selena Gomez (@selenagomez) on Jan 26, 2017 at 2:59am PST
Advertisement - Continue Reading Below The arrival of March means a lot of wonderful things are coming your way: spring break, warmer weather, and 13 Reasons Why , a series executive produced by the one and only Selena Gomez and her mom Mandy. All episodes will premiere on March 30, along with The Discovery , a Netflix original film about the afterlife starring Jason Segel, Robert Redford, and Rooney Mara. Speaking of Netflix originals, Amy Schumer has a new comedy special premiering on March 7, aptly called The Leather Special . Titles making their exit next month include all the Jaws movies and The Nanny Diaries , but you know how Netflix is — these movies will come back soon.
